e.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter17_EDIT-1392x1965.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter17_EDIT-1068x1507.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1417px) 100vw, 1417px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3562339" class="wp-caption-text">摘自“DFA 唱片：早年”：Tyler Pope，2003 年 10 月 9 日在 Bowery 宴会厅进行 LCD 音响系统试音 图片来源：Tim Soter </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3562340" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3562340" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3562340" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter21_EDIT.jpg" alt="摘自“DFA Records：早年”：2005 年 4 月 8 日，DFA Records 停工期间的派对。图片来源：Tim Soter" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter21_EDIT.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter21_EDIT-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter21_EDIT-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter21_EDIT-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter21_EDIT-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EXCLUSIVE_DFA_the_early_years_TimSoter21_EDIT-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3562340" class="wp-caption-text">摘自“DFA Records：早年”：2005 年 4 月 8 日，DFA Records 停工期间的派对。图片来源：Tim Soter</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《Meet Me In The Bathroom》</em>也对同一时代进行了探索，该作品几乎单枪匹马地促成了<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/indie-sleaze-revival-the-maccabees-the-horrors-white-heat-3162006">“独立音乐”现象</a>的出现——改编自前 NME 记者 Lizzy Goodman<em>在《New》中关于重生和摇滚乐的</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/strokes-lcd-new-york-meet-me-bathroom-lizzy-goodman-interview-2117913"><em>口述</em>历史书。</a> <em>《约克城2001-2011》</em>在被<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/meet-me-in-the-bathroom-review-dissecting-new-yorks-early-noughties-rock-revolution-3411510">拍成同名纪录片</a>之前上映。</p><p> LCD Soundsystem 最近完成了在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-trio-boro-new-york-city-residencies-buy-tickets-3507915">纽约市三个不同行政区为期 12 场的驻场演出</a>，他们在那里<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lcd-soundsystem-perform-one-touch-for-the-first-time-ever-at-new-york-residency-3542725">首次现场表演了《This Is Happening》中的《One Touch》</a> ，并翻唱了 The Pogues 的《Fairy》向 Shane MacGowan 致敬纽约故事》。</p><p>他们最终将于 12 月 30 日和 31 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-new-years-san-francisco-shows-3534190">在旧金山举行两场演出</a>，然后在 2024 年举行一系列欧洲演出，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-all-points-east-london-uk-tour-line-up-pixies-tickets-3551502">8 月 23 日在伦敦 All Points East 举行的头条新闻</a>。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fall-points-east-tickets%2Fartist%2F5245909" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取门票和更多信息。</p><p>该乐队最后一次发行音乐是在 2022 年，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-release-their-first-song-in-five-years-new-body-rhumba-3320310">一首名为“New Body Rhumba”的歌曲</a>是为诺亚·鲍姆巴赫 (Noah Baumbach) 的《白噪音》 <em>(White Noise)</em>的配乐而写的。他们最后一次发行全长专辑是在 2017 年，其中有《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lcd-soundsystem-american-dream-review-2133039-2133039">美国梦</a>》， <em>NME</em>称这张唱片“保留了概括地点和时间的不可思议的力量。这是一次谨慎的回归，而不是一次胜利——这证明了 LCD 音响系统非常具有 2017 年风格。”</p><p>这篇文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-these-exclusive-shots-from-new-photo-book-on-early-years-of-dfa-records-3562323">《看看这些来自 DFA 唱片公司早年的新写真集的独家照片》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
